name: Goth Building Style - Lord of The Rings style house, castle or landscape (gothbuilding)
description:
This style will do great if you want to make fantasy buildings in the style of "Lord of the rings", "Harry Potter" and "The Hobbit" movies.

Works well will simple prompts, but also advanced. List of example prompts in version description. Learning data is also attached.

Examples speak for themselves, please share how you used the style.
